    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Obakenori</i> you play as the titular character, a once powerful sea demon stuck in the form of an onigiri. Explore vivid environments and interact with its strange inhabitants as you gather ingredients for the Chef, uncover secrets of this world, and help Obakenori regain his former glory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073870/extras/c700a125ab128837eb02ac66895407a1.poster.avif?t=1761072623\" width=1014 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073870/extras/c700a125ab128837eb02ac66895407a1.webm?t=1761072623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073870/extras/c700a125ab128837eb02ac66895407a1.mp4?t=1761072623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 3D collectathon platformer inspired by the days of early 3D gaming. Created by a solo developer, the world of Obakenori is teeming with playful (but not always friendly) creatures, hidden treasures, puzzles and of course, food related quests for the Chef!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073870/extras/86caea50b8745db124a54dbf8642410d.poster.avif?t=1761072623\" width=1014 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073870/extras/86caea50b8745db124a54dbf8642410d.webm?t=1761072623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073870/extras/86caea50b8745db124a54dbf8642410d.mp4?t=1761072623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock a range of abilities to help traverse the world and defeat (tasty) foes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth, satisfying platforming as you explore new locations and navigate interesting puzzles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the cast of characters, some who want to guide you, and some who want your power for themselves!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the mysteries of who Obakenori is, his 'family' and how he ended up as a rice ball!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a friendship with the Chef and Mechanic, although things might start off rocky!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
